notes: England 50 in 37 minutes off 57 balls (8.1 overs) 7x4
A Flintoff 50 in 97 minutes off 66 balls 5x4 and 2x6
PD Collingwood 50 in 75 minutes off 62 balls 8x4
England 300 in 202 minutes off 314 balls, 34x4 and 5x6
Record England 5th wicket partnership of 174 between Flintoff and Collingwood
Collingwood dropped by Kaif off Harbhajan Singh on 12, England 135/4, 30th over
Flintoff dropped by Balaji off Pathan on 80, England 245/4 in the 45th over
M Kaif 50 in 91 minutes off 68 balls, 8x4
50 partnership, 10th wicket, in 34 minutes off 49 balls (Singh 31, Balaji 15)
Record 10th wicket partnership for India against England
Highest 10th wicket partnership for India between Harbhajan Singh and Balaji

milestones.description: Paul Collingwood and Flintoff's 174-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 142 between Robin Smith and Graham Thorpe
Harbhajan and Balaji's 64-run partnership is IND's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 62 between Srinath and Ajay Jadeja
